{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一回\"死神帖与情人箭\"开篇，武林中突然出现神秘暗器\"情人箭\"，每逢月圆之夜便有人丧命。仁义四侠中的谭啸风赶往保定城通知狮兄，又奔赴望都城寻找张大哥，却目睹张大哥已惨死于情人箭下。仁义四侠之二魏子云在青海塔尔寺跳神盛典中被骷髅恶鬼伏杀。四侠之四胡天麟在塞外甜水井边发现镖队惨案，最终亦遭伏杀，尸身上方现死神帖。场景转至杭州西溪，展化雨之子展梦白在武士堂与林软红交谈，得知父亲失踪消息。神医秦瘦翁携女秦琪现身，展梦白与秦琪发生冲突。崂山三雁之三贺君侠飞报展化雨身中情人箭、命在垂危，全武林人人自危。秦瘦翁以\"无义务救人\"为由拒绝出诊，展梦白忍辱道歉，恳求秦瘦翁救父。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谭啸风",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "text": "狮兄可在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "紫面大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "紫面大汉",
      "listener": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "text": "谭三哥，你怎么来了！请快进来喝两杯热酒。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谭啸风",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "text": "狮兄可曾接到了死神帖么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谭啸风",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "text": "此地虽然无月，但今日却是月圆之期，正是'死神帖'与'情人箭'肆虐之时，狮兄此地如无变故，我便要乘夜赶到望都城去！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "紫面大汉",
      "listener": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "text": "死神帖出没之地，无人可测，谭三哥你如此奔波，还不是徒劳往返么！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谭啸风",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "text": "自从'三湘大侠'紫平死在'情人箭'下后，我兄弟四人，便发誓要查出这一帖一箭的来历，此举成功之望虽极渺茫，但我兄弟却不得不尽人事以听天命，好歹要为武林江湖间保存几分生机元气。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谭啸风",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "text": "狮兄保重，我走了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "紫面大汉",
      "listener": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "text": "谭三哥且慢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "紫面大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仁义四侠，当真名下无虚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谭啸风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "text": "张兄，小弟谭啸风前来拜访！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谭啸风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "text": "张大哥，你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谭啸风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张大哥，小弟来迟了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_ce_ce_de_sheng_yin",
      "speaker_name": "阴恻恻的声音",
      "listener": "char_tan_xiao_feng",
      "text": "还赶得上！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": "char_ma_guan_lao_ren",
      "text": "前面的可是'仁义四侠'中的魏子云魏二哥么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_guan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻冠老人",
      "listener": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "text": "小弟正欲入关，路经此地，倒是魏二哥你的侠踪怎会来到这里？却令小弟费解。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": "char_ma_guan_lao_ren",
      "text": "我久闻此间的喇嘛高僧，俱都身怀令人不可思议的密宗绝技，早就想来见识一番，再者……我还想看看已如瘟疫一般在武林中肆虐的'死神帖'与'情人箭'，是否已蔓延到此间。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_guan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻冠老人",
      "listener": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "text": "我虽远在边疆，但也从来自中原的游侠口中，隐约听到一些有关这一帖一箭的故事，想不到魏二哥你竟也是为了此事而来，难道这一帖一箭，真有传说中那般可怖。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": "char_ma_guan_lao_ren",
      "text": "小弟一生之中，从未听闻过有'情人箭'那样神秘可怖的暗器，不到半年，武林中已有数十位成名露脸的英雄死在这'情人箭'下，而直到此刻为止，武林间竟还没有一人知道它的来历。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_guan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻冠老人",
      "listener": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "text": "区区两枝短箭，竟有如此可怖，这当真是令人不可想像之事，难道它上面附有剧毒，难道这剧毒无人可解？即使它是世上最毒的暗器，武功登堂入室之人，也该能够闪避的呀？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": "char_ma_guan_lao_ren",
      "text": "此事我又何尝不是百思不得其解，就连在武林中号称第一的毒药暗器名家，蜀中唐氏兄弟，都在三月之前，死在'情人箭'下。但江湖中倒绝非无人可解此毒，但也只有一人而已，若非当心中箭，三个时辰之中，送到此人之处，十日之内，便可康复。只是那'情人箭'出没无常，今日在东，明日在西，能得此人救治的，至今也不过只有三五人而已。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_zi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "魏子云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_mian_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "左面一人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "text": "情人箭！如此凶毒可怖的暗器，居然称做'情人箭'，此人也未免太尖刻了些。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_mian_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "右面一人",
      "listener": "char_zuo_mian_yi_ren",
      "text": "月圆花好之时，鸳鸯两箭齐来，箭上之毒，毒性又是一阴一阳，中箭之人，十九俱是伤在心上……此箭称作情人，岂非十分恰当？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_mian_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "朝阳兄",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "text": "无论是否恰当，我却不愿伤心，胡四弟，我劝你还是随我一齐回到瓜州，歇息半日，一齐回江南的好。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_mian_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "胡天麟",
      "listener": "char_le_zhao_yang",
      "text": "朝阳兄，你尽管自回瓜州，我却要到敦煌左近去走上一趟，看看那位'情人'的秋波，有没有送到这塞上的仙境来。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_zhao_yang",
      "speaker_name": "乐朝阳",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "text": "你们仁义四侠，终年为他人奔波，难怪你直到今日，还是孤家寡人一个，而哥哥我却已是绿叶成荫子满枝了，昔日的雄风豪气，至今也……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_zhao_yang",
      "speaker_name": "乐朝阳",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "text": "今夜又是十五了，胡四弟，你……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡天麟",
      "listener": "char_le_zhao_yang",
      "text": "朝阳兄，你只管放心，我胡天麟孤家寡人，哪有'情人'会照顾我？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡天麟",
      "listener": "char_le_zhao_yang",
      "text": "三月之后，江南再见，到那时我要让你这塞外的野人，好好尝一尝江南名厨的风味！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡天麟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然又是情人箭……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡天麟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "西北快刀宋海萍……唉，武林中又弱一人！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tian_lin",
      "speaker_name": "胡天麟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_chuan_de_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "摇船的汉子",
      "listener": "char_du_juan",
      "text": "杜……杜鹃，你……你又在唱……唱什么？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_juan",
      "speaker_name": "杜鹃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在唱小结巴，去采茶……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_suo_yi_yu_weng",
      "speaker_name": "蓑衣渔翁",
      "listener": "char_du_juan",
      "text": "好没规矩的丫头，看到展公子，也不请安问好。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_juan",
      "speaker_name": "杜鹃",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展公子您好。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_suo_yi_yu_weng",
      "speaker_name": "蓑衣渔翁",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展公子可是又要到'武士堂'去喝茶么？今日不是月圆日，那里的人定必不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_suo_yi_yu_weng",
      "speaker_name": "蓑衣渔翁",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "稍等若有鲜鱼，我叫鹃儿送两尾去给公子下酒。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "梦白，你怎地到此刻才来？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "text": "林兄，可曾听到家父的消息？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我已时刻俱在留意，昨日'崂山三雁'经过这里，他兄弟三人来自浙东，那里也无人见到过令尊的侠踪，但他们却在天台山下，见到'塞上大侠'乐朝阳，和一个年纪颇轻的武当道人，行色匆匆，往南而去，似乎是直奔雁荡山的方向。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "text": "乐大侠与我四叔交谊非浅，四叔惨变后，他必然会有行动。那'崂山三雁'是否便是以三柄吴钩剑成名武林的贺氏兄弟，他三人行色如此匆忙，为的又是什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "赶回家去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "都回家了，都回家了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不回家又怎样，自从魏二侠殒于青海，谭三侠折于保定，胡四侠在'甜水井'边丧身后，武林中更是人人自危，保命为先，就连'华山七莺'每年必办的'花朝大会'，今年都宣告流产，唉！梦白，不瞒你说，我若非要将此楼留做江南群侠的交换消息之地，我也早已收山退隐了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "梦白，我劝你近日也要稍为收敛些的好，据目前情况看来，那'情人箭'绝非一人所有，可怕的是，你根本无从猜测谁的怀中藏有这可怖的暗器，说不定就是你身侧之人，也说不定是……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "text": "说不定我展梦白身上就有几双'情人箭'……林兄，你可要小心了，快替我拿酒来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人是谁？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "楼角老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小孩子，你不认得我么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "眼疏得很！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "楼角老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小孩子说话总要放慎重些，你纵然有个好爹爹，也不必张牙舞爪地来讨人厌。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "梦白，你何苦，快坐下来。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "老年人说话也该放慎重些，你纵然有几把年纪，也没有什么值得傲人之处。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "楼角老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好孩子，居然敢教训起我来了，你以后就难道没有求我之处么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "梦白，你怎地如此气盛，得罪了他老人家……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹，是谁要教训你老人家？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "是你么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_qin_qi",
      "text": "不错，是我，难道只有你爹爹可以胡乱骂人，别人就说不得话么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秦姑娘……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "秦老先生，这位展兄乃是武林中素有'及时雨'之称的展化雨展大侠的令郎，今日本是小事，何苦……唉！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_qin_qi",
      "text": "我虽不喜与妇人女子一般见识，但……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "但什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_qin_qi",
      "text": "但你若再向我面前走上一步，今日我就要替你家的尊长来教训教训你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好好。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我倒要看看——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "text": "要打架就请出去，哼哼，这算什么，难道区区一副对联，就可以吓得倒人么？姑娘喜欢在哪里动手，就在哪里动手？谁管得着我？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_qin_qi",
      "text": "秦姑娘可知道这副对联是谁写的么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林第一侠……哼哼，好大的口气，谁是武——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "秦瘦翁",
      "listener": "char_qin_qi",
      "text": "琪儿，休得无礼，既有大侠的墨宝在此，你还不快给我坐下！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好了好了，今日小弟做东，请各位都喝一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "除非你不下楼……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_qin_qi",
      "text": "便是此刻……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "text": "君侠兄，什么事如此惊惶？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪一位是展公子，哪一位是秦瘦翁老先生？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "text": "在下便是展梦白，贺大侠有何……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展……兄，展公子，令尊……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "text": "家父怎样了？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展老前辈已身受重伤，命在垂危……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "被谁所伤？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "情……人……箭！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "让他喝下去！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展老前辈虽然身中'情人箭'，但幸而便在城外，在下发现又早，距离此刻，还不到两个时辰，若能立刻寻到秦瘦翁秦老先生尚属可救，只是方才二哥去寻秦老先生，却说不在！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "text": "不要紧，我爹爹在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "前辈你便是秦老先生么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "秦瘦翁",
      "listener": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "快请前辈移驾到……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "speaker_name": "林软红",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "秦老先生，救人一命，胜造七级浮屠，何况展老前辈一生急公好义，济人之难，不遗余力……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "秦瘦翁",
      "listener": "char_lin_ruan_hong",
      "text": "展化雨的儿子在这里，要你代他多什么话？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "秦老先生，方才是……是我错了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻已近两个时辰，救人如救火，再迟就来不及了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "秦瘦翁",
      "listener": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "text": "你若敢在老夫身上沾上一根手指，从此那'情人箭'之毒就无人能解了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "你是走还是不走？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "秦琪",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "爹爹……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "秦瘦翁",
      "listener": "char_qin_qi",
      "text": "不要多口！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "speaker_name": "贺君侠",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "你再不走，就莫要怪我贺君侠无礼了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "speaker_name": "秦瘦翁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽有救人解毒之能，却没有救人解毒的义务……这两尾鲜鱼不错，琪儿，带回去给爹爹下酒。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_juan",
      "speaker_name": "杜鹃",
      "listener": "char_qin_shou_weng",
      "text": "这两尾鱼不卖的，是爹爹叫我……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_jun_jie",
      "speaker_name": "贺君杰",
      "listener": "char_he_jun_xia",
      "text": "老三，找着秦老先生了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    }
  ],
